news.title: SC bars 'apartmentalization' of residential units in Chandigarh
news.para: A bench of Justices B R Gavai and B V Nagarathna slammed the Chandigarh administration for "blindly sanctioning" building plans and said it is apparent from them that they are in effect converting one dwelling unit into three apartments.

news.title: Gujarat government brings new rules to stop NRG property fraud
news.para: From now on, an NRG or individual residing outside the state, who delegates authority to their representatives to execute the sale of a property, will have to send an additional document declaring s/he was alive at the time of the sale.

news.title: NGT serves notice to agencies, government over flats on forest land in DLF-3
news.para: Retired Gurugram forest officer Rajinder Krishan Sharma and city resident Pawan Kumar Bansal alleged that 4,484 sqm of forest land in Sikanderpur-Nathupur Bundh area was diverted to build Ambience Island Lagoon Apartments in 2008 in defiance of the Forest Conservation Act, 1980.
